the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your arsenal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect blueprints and craft new <strong>weapons</strong> and <strong>upgrades</strong> in order to fight more effectively. Each new item you acquire will give you more options and increase your chances of survival.</p>",
